{"data":{"site":{"meta":{"title":"Yentsen Liu","description":"Interface/Empowerment/Democracy Design Portfolio by Yentsen Liu","url":"https://yentsenliu.com","author":"Yentsen Liu","twitter":"ansinlau","adsense":""}},"post":{"id":"f5088d76-ffae-58d0-96ec-7611ef3b91e7","html":"<hr>\n<h1>How design could help interactively visualise data, and how design can lower the threshold of transforming raw data into conprehensive information?</h1>\n<p>By redesigning the user interface of Statfin, the official statistics database of Finland, the project aims to demonstrate how design could help interactively visualise data, and how design can lower the threshold of transforming raw data into conprehensive information. It could be helpful not only to the citizens, but also to the government employees who need to make data-based reports. This transformation could also provide a basis for strengthening civil society. </p>\n<h5>Responsibility and skill</h5>\n<p>I worked independently on <strong>UI/UX Design</strong> and on <strong>web development</strong> for showcasing the project at Visualizing Knowledge 2018 Conference, Finland. </p>\n<p><strong>Software</strong>: Skecth App, Framer | <strong>Tech stack</strong>: HTML, SASS, and Javascript</p>\n<hr>\n<img style=\"\" src=\"/img-1-c64ce6302f15d3e0399ea27340737810.gif\" alt=\"The concept of platform hosting the livable experience of Taiwanese design.\">\n<figcaption>A glance at the interface after (left) and before (right) the redesign</figcaption>\n<hr>\n<h3>Discover</h3>\n<h3>Deliver</h3>\n<h4>Showcase</h4>\n<p>This was a showcase work at Visualizing Knowledge 2018 Conference, Finland. </p>\n<hr>\n\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-bottom: 1.0725rem;; max-width: 1440px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 57.847222222222214%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\">\n      <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\" alt=\"a screenshot of the showcase\" title=\"\" src=\"/static/img-2-535a2c2fbb329c8f925b5d5169e95f0b-daa98.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/img-2-535a2c2fbb329c8f925b5d5169e95f0b-09631.jpg 500w,\n/static/img-2-535a2c2fbb329c8f925b5d5169e95f0b-d85d3.jpg 1000w,\n/static/img-2-535a2c2fbb329c8f925b5d5169e95f0b-daa98.jpg 1440w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1440px) 100vw, 1440px\">\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n<figure class=\"grid-image\"><div class=\"grid-image-grid\" style=\"\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(48%, 1fr));\n          \">\n\n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-bottom: 1.0725rem;; max-width: 1302px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 66.58986175115209%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"img 3\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/img-3-150531a923cbb14f779a93e30abea2a5-5f8e5.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/img-3-150531a923cbb14f779a93e30abea2a5-97180.jpg 500w,\n/static/img-3-150531a923cbb14f779a93e30abea2a5-5b02c.jpg 1000w,\n/static/img-3-150531a923cbb14f779a93e30abea2a5-5f8e5.jpg 1302w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1302px) 100vw, 1302px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n\n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-bottom: 1.0725rem;; max-width: 1215px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 66.66666666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"img 4\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/img-4-dfb27d511b4ad9dce3f51b9dc6c00b4f-6418a.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/img-4-dfb27d511b4ad9dce3f51b9dc6c00b4f-35acd.jpg 500w,\n/static/img-4-dfb27d511b4ad9dce3f51b9dc6c00b4f-5e558.jpg 1000w,\n/static/img-4-dfb27d511b4ad9dce3f51b9dc6c00b4f-6418a.jpg 1215w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1215px) 100vw, 1215px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n</div></figure>\n<hr>\n<p>You can visit <a href=\"https://yentsenliu.com/redesign_statfin/\" target=\"blank\">the webpage showcasing the work</a> at Visualizing Knowledge 2018 here. (Unfortunately, the mobile version of this page is not availabe because the webpage was designed for showcasing on high resolution display.)</p>\n<hr>\n<img style=\"\" src=\"/img-5-c8b4b3dc590efc64e172de9bc893fcb0.gif\" alt=\"The concept of platform hosting the livable experience of Taiwanese design.\">\n<hr>\n<h4>Report</h4>\n<p>There is also a report introducing the design in details available on <a href=\"https://yentsenliu.gitbook.io/redesign-statfin/\" target=\"blank\">Gitbook</a>.</p>\n<p>In this report, a proposal for bettering the Statfin database is demonstrated. The report comprises the following parts: </p>\n<ul>\n<li>Problem Framing: to illustrate a framework of the problems existing in current online services; to demonstrate on what basis I understand the services provided by Statistics Finland, and how did I conduct my research. </li>\n<li>Redesign Statfin: the proposal of redesigning the online data bank of Statistics Finland. </li>\n<li>Limitation and Discussion: to summarize the report by showing the limitation, and providing some insight into the further development.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>I was also invited to have an informal presentation of this work at Statistics Finland (Tilastokeskus), the statistics authority of Finland, in 24th May, 2018.</p>\n<hr>\n\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-bottom: 1.0725rem;; max-width: 2000px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 31.666666666666664%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\">\n      <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\" alt=\"some snap shots of the conference and the visit to Statistics Finland\" title=\"\" src=\"/static/img-7-4cbe5f5cfd3c48c4687852b5fa9a5f71-7874f.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/img-7-4cbe5f5cfd3c48c4687852b5fa9a5f71-cf602.jpg 500w,\n/static/img-7-4cbe5f5cfd3c48c4687852b5fa9a5f71-ec5b1.jpg 1000w,\n/static/img-7-4cbe5f5cfd3c48c4687852b5fa9a5f71-7874f.jpg 2000w,\n/static/img-7-4cbe5f5cfd3c48c4687852b5fa9a5f71-b35a9.jpg 3000w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\">\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  ","frontmatter":{"layout":"post","title":"Official Statistics in The Age of Data","path":"/statfin/","category":"design for interface","tags":["UI","Prototyping","Data Visualization"],"description":"Showcase work at Visualizing Knowledge 2018 Conference, Finland.","date":"2018/05/03","image":{"childImageSharp":{"fixed":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","width":500,"height":357,"src":"/static/statfin-0b460aab0672e44e7